@startuml application-state-diagram
title DVLD Application Lifecycle - State Diagram

skinparam shadowing false
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam state {
  BackgroundColor #F8FAFC
  BorderColor #334155
  FontColor #111827
}

[*] --> New : Submit Application

state "In Review / Processing" as InReview
state "Rejected / Blocked" as RejectedBlocked

New --> InReview : Validate Application
New --> Cancelled : Cancel Application
New --> RejectedBlocked : Reject Invalid Application

InReview --> Completed : Complete Required Workflow
InReview --> Cancelled : Cancel Application
InReview --> RejectedBlocked : Reject Invalid Application

RejectedBlocked --> InReview : Correct And Revalidate

Completed --> [*]
Cancelled --> [*]

note right of RejectedBlocked
Used when validation, eligibility,
duplicate active application, payment,
or workflow prerequisites fail.
end note

@enduml
